        public static java.awt.image.BufferedImage randomCropImage(java.awt.image.BufferedImage img)
        随机裁剪，因为正常裁剪并不复杂。 裁剪部分大小由TFUtils.cropRate指定 random crop, since normal cropping is not complicated. crop portion is specified by TFUtils.cropRate
        返回:
        来自img的随机选择区域 a randomly selected region from img

      • checkAccuracy

        public static double[] checkAccuracy(java.lang.String resultFile,
                                     java.lang.String labelFile)
        以原始的方式检查预测准确率。 Check accuracy in a foolproof way. 
         if(path.indexOf(label)!=-1)correct[index]++;
        参数:
        resultFile -
        labelFile -
        返回:
        double[classIndex]=accuracy
        精度=（机器判断正确）/（机器认为是在这个类）
        即1-精度=假阳性率(?)
        accuracy = (machine got it right)/(machine thought it to be in this class)
        i.e. 1-accuracy = false positive rate
